WEBVTT

00:03:57.812 --> 00:04:00.833
n'ime obodo ndi no n'ime ya ruru 
nde nari abuo.

00:04:02.422 --> 00:04:03.891
N'Africa niile,

00:04:03.915 --> 00:04:07.818
iri itoolu n'ime otu nari nmadu a naghi
e nweta ezigbo ogwu ahu ike.

00:04:08.681 --> 00:04:10.434
N'ihi nkea,

00:04:10.458 --> 00:04:13.462
anyi n'anwu n'ekwughi okwu,

00:04:13.486 --> 00:04:17.150
na kwa i kpa oke a na-akpa n'etiti 
ndi ahu di na ndi ahu adighi.

00:04:17.498 --> 00:04:22.173
Agwa anyi na-akpa mgbe o bula ekwutere 
okwu isi izu oke, bu nke ikpa oke,

00:04:22.844 --> 00:04:24.046
amaghi ihe,

00:04:24.535 --> 00:04:25.713
amam ikpe,

00:04:26.134 --> 00:04:27.340
egwu,

00:04:27.934 --> 00:04:29.220
na kwa iwe.